# most used vscode shortcuts

### Access Explorer

`cmnd + shift + e`

### Open new file in a folder via the explorer

`shift + t`

### Send window to right/left

`control + cmnd + >/<`

### Send focus to right/left

`option + cmnd + >/<`

### Split terminal

`cmnd + \`

- Send focus same as file

